title: Comedy competition semi-finals Nov. 20 at Skagit Valley Casino Resort
text:
October 21, 2015 Comedy competition semi-finals Nov. 20 at Skagit Valley Casino Resort Bret Michaels’ True Grit Tour is at 8 p.m. Oct. 23 and 24 at the Skagit Valley Casino Resort’s Pacific Showroom in Bow. Tickets are $55 and $60. CHRISTINE A. ELLIS Courtesy to The Bellingham Herald i Order Reprint of this Story THIS WEEK
